= ABOUT

Transforms PubMed Central's NLM Archiving and Interchange DTD 3.0 XML
(NXML) [1] into plain text with MediaWiki syntax [2].

[1] http://dtd.nlm.nih.gov/
[2] http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting

= STATUS

"Experimental" would be an euphemism. Currently not really usable.


= EXAMPLE

* Get the file list:
  ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/pmc/file_list.txt
* Find publication file by the Pubmed ID e.g. 
  $ grep 2566812 file_list.txt
  1e/f3/PLoS_ONE-3-10-2566812.tar.gz	PLoS ONE. 2008 Oct 17; 3(10):e3229	PMC2566812
* append the this to the URL ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/pmc/ 
  => ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/pmc/1e/f3/PLoS_ONE-3-10-2566812.tar.gz
* Untar the file
  $ tar xfz PLoS_ONE-3-10-2566812.tar.gz
* Use a XSLT processor (e.g. xsltproc) to apply the XSL file to the NXML file
  $ xsltproc pcm2mediawiki.xsl PLoS\ ONE/3-10/pe3229-2566812/pone.0003229.nxml
  